[SPEAKER_00] sin Božiji,

198
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:27,379
[SPEAKER_00] jer me treba svaki dan.

199
00:15:27,379 --> 00:15:30,820
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono,

200
00:15:30,820 --> 00:15:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] baš ako se posjetiš

201
00:15:32,559 --> 00:15:33,379
[SPEAKER_00] obitelji,

202
