206
00:15:40,899 --> 00:15:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] da je,

207
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

208
00:15:43,539 --> 00:15:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] obitelj jedno zlatno tele,

209
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:46,419
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ti sad, ono,

210
00:15:46,419 --> 00:15:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] to isto ljudi znaju rajdu,

211
00:15:47,779 --> 00:15:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] hvate se obitelji

212
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] i to zapravo bude bijeg od sebe,

213
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:53,159
[SPEAKER_00] od dubljeg služenja,

214
00:15:53,159 --> 00:15:55,200
[SPEAKER_00] bijeg od posloženosti,

215
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] ne, o tome ne govorim.

216
00:15:56,759 --> 00:15:58,620
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, stvari su posložene,

217
00:15:58,620 --> 00:15:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] zdravo je,

218
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:01,919
[SPEAKER_00] i kad se ti tako daš obitelji,

219
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] ti zapravo vidiš koliko tebe,

220
00:16:03,679 --> 00:16:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] jedan član tvoje crkve,

221
00:16:06,639 --> 00:16:07,259
[SPEAKER_00] kućne,

222
00:16:07,259 --> 00:16:10,259
[SPEAKER_00] koga ti je Bog stavio na povjerenje,

223
00:16:10,639 --> 00:16:12,419
[SPEAKER_00] tebi, velikom evangelizatoru,

224
00:16:12,419 --> 00:16:14,220
