225
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:15,820
[SPEAKER_00] koji nemate možda dar djece,

226
00:16:15,820 --> 00:16:16,919
[SPEAKER_00] dao ti je ženu,

227
00:16:16,919 --> 00:16:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] dao ti je nekog ukućena s kim živiš,

228
00:16:19,259 --> 00:16:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] možda sa roditeljima još neko živi,

229
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,200
[SPEAKER_00] sa starijima,

230
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] sa bratom, sestvom, nebitnom,

231
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:25,240
[SPEAKER_00] dao ti je gospodin.

232
00:16:26,299 --> 00:16:28,879
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, daj mu se.

233
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mu se daš do kraja srcem,

234
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] uz Božiju pomoć,

235
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] onda zapravo vidiš koliko to troši,

236
00:16:36,179 --> 00:16:37,919
[SPEAKER_00] koliko te to uzima,

237
00:16:37,919 --> 00:16:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je to zahtjevno,

238
00:16:39,559 --> 00:16:41,679
[SPEAKER_00] i tu se događaju procesi

239
00:16:41,679 --> 00:16:42,820
[SPEAKER_00] o kojima ću pričati.

240
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:47,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon moga rafa dolazi moja Terezija,

241
00:16:47,299 --> 00:16:49,899
[SPEAKER_00] ona je sad ušla u šestu godinu,

242
00:16:49,899 --> 00:16:52,620
[SPEAKER_00] to je zjenica moga oka,

243
00:16:52,620 --> 00:16:54,120
[SPEAKER_00] posebna ljubav.

244
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dajana opet mora strogo mirovati.

245
00:16:57,519 --> 00:17:00,379
[SPEAKER_00] Dajana je lavica sa jednog boka,

246
00:17:00,379 --> 00:17:02,600
[SPEAKER_00] jedno djete na drugi bok,

247
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] s drugim djetetom,

248
00:17:03,539 --> 00:17:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] isto strogo mirovanje,

249
00:17:05,099 --> 00:17:07,259
[SPEAKER_00] isto se povlačim iz zajednice,

250
00:17:07,259 --> 00:17:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] isto se povlačim iz zajednice,

251
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] isto Bogu dajem za žrtvu

252
00:17:12,599 --> 00:17:14,799
[SPEAKER_00] i služim svojoj obitelji.

253
00:17:14,799 --> 00:17:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ulazim u ulogu sluge,

254
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:22,660
[SPEAKER_00] ulazim ono što pater sebo zna,

255
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:24,200
[SPEAKER_00] rečka smo puno puta pričali,

256
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,779
[SPEAKER_00] ona četvrta Isusova uloga,

257
00:17:26,779 --> 00:17:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] trpećeg sluge.

258
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] I evo,

259
00:17:30,700 --> 00:17:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] obitelj se razvija,

260
00:17:32,099 --> 00:17:33,380
