261
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] Što vam s ovim hoću reći?

262
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Djeca te trebaju i žena te trebaju svaki dan.

263
00:17:40,180 --> 00:17:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ih je stavio na tvoj put,

264
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,779
