265
00:17:42,779 --> 00:17:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] I sada u tome životu sa njima

266
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] počne se događati prava preobrazma moga srca.

267
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:52,859
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja koji evangeliziram,

268
00:17:52,859 --> 00:17:56,019
