269
00:17:56,019 --> 00:17:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] događa se,

270
00:17:57,299 --> 00:18:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti daje milost vidljivih uspjeha,

271
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] da vidi šta On čini,

272
00:18:01,900 --> 00:18:05,700
