273
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi znaju najbolji dio mene

274
00:18:07,500 --> 00:18:09,140
[SPEAKER_00] i ulaziš u jednu,

275
00:18:09,140 --> 00:18:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] možda je nesvjesnu zamku

276
00:18:10,579 --> 00:18:12,319
