279
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:18,240
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ulaziš u tu uholos da si ti netko.

280
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] I onda Bog šta radi?

281
00:18:19,900 --> 00:18:21,980
