289
00:18:35,900 --> 00:18:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] I na jednom događa se,

290
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] evo, klinici su veliki.

291
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:44,099
