[SPEAKER_00] koji imaju puno djece,

293
00:18:45,180 --> 00:18:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] više nego troje.

294
00:18:46,519 --> 00:18:48,839
[SPEAKER_00] Evo tu je moj brat Marko i Sanja,

295
00:18:48,839 --> 00:18:50,299
[SPEAKER_00] su voditelji zajednice,

296
00:18:50,299 --> 00:18:51,099
