300
00:18:56,859 --> 00:18:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, znam da ima ljudi

301
00:18:59,579 --> 00:19:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji imaju više djece,

302
00:19:00,619 --> 00:19:03,259
[SPEAKER_00] no evo, ovi moje troje,

303
00:19:03,259 --> 00:19:04,680
[SPEAKER_00] ono, stvarno te,

304
00:19:04,799 --> 00:19:06,000
