308
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] kao što vodiš zajednicu,

309
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:15,799
[SPEAKER_00] imaš osam godina jednog čovjeka

310
00:19:15,799 --> 00:19:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] pored sebe.

311
00:19:16,519 --> 00:19:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjeka koji te non-stop traži.

312
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:21,019
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjeka koji te non-stop treba

313
00:19:21,019 --> 00:19:22,839
[SPEAKER_00] i kom ti trebaš dati ono

314
00:19:22,839 --> 00:19:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] što Bog je namijenio da mu daš.

315
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,259
[SPEAKER_00] I tu gospodin pokazuje,

316
00:19:27,259 --> 00:19:28,339
[SPEAKER_00] okej,

317
00:19:28,339 --> 00:19:32,200
