329
00:19:57,359 --> 00:19:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] kao moje djete.

330
00:19:58,220 --> 00:19:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] A ja kažem,

331
00:19:59,380 --> 00:20:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] da, da, dobro,

332
00:20:00,039 --> 00:20:00,759
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, okej,

333
00:20:00,759 --> 00:20:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] depusti me na miru čovječanom.

334
00:20:02,619 --> 00:20:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] Pa imam posla,

335
00:20:04,019 --> 00:20:05,200
