342
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] ako sad mogu reći,

343
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] ne budem kontradiktoran.

344
00:20:17,279 --> 00:20:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] ono, slabi smo,

345
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] da se razumijemo,

346
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] ograničene smo.

347
00:20:20,839 --> 00:20:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, ako se to nastavlja,

348
00:20:23,539 --> 00:20:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] ako ja ne vidim

349
00:20:24,940 --> 00:20:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] da tu griješim,

350
00:20:26,539 --> 00:20:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] ako ja ne vidim

351
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:29,920
