[SPEAKER_00] ja kad god bi išao iz Osijeka za Zagreb,

569
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih svek molio

570
00:26:57,420 --> 00:27:00,180
[SPEAKER_00] i prikazivao sve te ljude po imenu gospodino.

571
00:27:00,180 --> 00:27:05,279
[SPEAKER_00] Onda bi mi ponekad gospodin za neke određene ljude dao jasnoću

572
00:27:05,279 --> 00:27:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] s čim se bore,

573
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] s čim se muče

574
00:27:08,279 --> 00:27:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] i dao mi do znanja,

575
00:27:11,039 --> 00:27:11,339
[SPEAKER_00] pardon,

576
00:27:11,339 --> 00:27:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] da im to, ono, mogu reći

577
00:27:14,279 --> 00:27:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] i da će se tu dogoditi otvaranje njihovog srca i otvaranje uma.

578
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] I zaista, to bi tako bilo.

579
00:27:21,460 --> 00:27:25,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ti ljudi su znali stati

580
00:27:25,259 --> 00:27:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] i kapitulirati

581
00:27:27,039 --> 00:27:30,359
[SPEAKER_00] pred jasnoćom da je Bog živ

582
00:27:30,359 --> 00:27:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] kroz neku spoznoju

583
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] u kojim je gospodin dao njima stanje,

584
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,160
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem se nalaze

585
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] i konkretno vrlo jasno s čim se muče.

586
00:27:37,519 --> 00:27:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja su oni,

587
00:27:39,380 --> 00:27:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] a svi su, inače,

588
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] bitna stvar,

589
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] svi su znali da sam vjernik.

590
00:27:43,519 --> 00:27:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad sam došao pomoći mati u Gideonu,

591
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam Matije rekao,

592
00:27:48,900 --> 00:27:50,339
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam ne želim sakrivat.

593
00:27:50,339 --> 00:27:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja, ono,

594
00:27:52,039 --> 00:27:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] jasno je da neću mahat Biblijom

595
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] u firmi,

596
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:57,680
[SPEAKER_00] niti Matija bi sumnio da bi napreku gluposti

597
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] da se poznajemo,

598
00:27:58,500 --> 00:28:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja sam rekao,

599
00:28:00,039 --> 00:28:00,759
[SPEAKER_00] čuj, ono,

600
00:28:00,759 --> 00:28:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] u toj prezentaciji

601
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:04,440
[SPEAKER_00] mojih nekih

602
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] komunikativnih vještina

603
00:28:06,940 --> 00:28:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] koju ja trebam ponuditi

604
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:09,160
[SPEAKER_00] tvojim ljudima,

605
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,799
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim da je pošteno,

606
00:28:10,799 --> 00:28:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] da oni znaju da sam ja vjernik.

607
00:28:12,819 --> 00:28:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerojatno će me googlat nešto

608
00:28:14,599 --> 00:28:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjet će tamo svjedočanstva,

609
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,200
[SPEAKER_00] svašta nešto

610
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ono,

611
00:28:18,599 --> 00:28:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] to je to.

612
00:28:19,019 --> 00:28:19,859
[SPEAKER_00] Jel ti to u redu?

613
00:28:19,859 --> 00:28:20,400
[SPEAKER_00] U redu je,

614
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] slobodno reci.

615
00:28:21,779 --> 00:28:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] Tako su oni svi znali da sam ja vjernik.

616
00:28:23,599 --> 00:28:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] I onda tu se počeo otvarati njihov um.

617
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:28,660
[SPEAKER_00] Počeli su kapitulirati

618
00:28:28,660 --> 00:28:29,680
[SPEAKER_00] i rekli su,

619
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] okej, ovo ne možemo objasniti.

620
00:28:31,220 --> 00:28:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje nešto postoji.

621
00:28:32,819 --> 00:28:33,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

622
00:28:33,660 --> 00:28:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se vratim na temo obitelji,

623
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] to ih nije promijenilo.

624
00:28:37,279 --> 00:28:38,859
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta ih je promijenilo?

625
00:28:38,859 --> 00:28:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je promijenilo njihova srca

626
00:28:41,079 --> 00:28:42,200
[SPEAKER_00] do dana današnje,

627
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] kad više ne radim,

628
00:28:43,140 --> 00:28:44,220
[SPEAKER_00] da se čujem sa njima

629
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:46,740
[SPEAKER_00] i ti ljudi žele da imamo razgovore,

630
00:28:46,740 --> 00:28:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] žele da se družimo,

631
00:28:48,099 --> 00:28:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] da imamo jedno bratsko ozrače sada.

632
00:28:51,779 --> 00:28:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] Njihova srca je počela mijati ljubav.

633
00:28:54,900 --> 00:28:59,400
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su vidjeli mene da razgovaram sa njima

634
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] sa jednakom pažnjom

635
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:04,200
[SPEAKER_00] i ljubavlju i interesiranjem,

636
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] kao što razgovaram sa Matijom,

637
00:29:06,519 --> 00:29:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] koji je CEO bio firme.

638
00:29:08,500 --> 00:29:14,200
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjeli su da razgovaram sa kršćanima

639
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] u toj firmi,

640
00:29:15,380 --> 00:29:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] s kojima sam krenio u neku molitvena aktivnosti,

641
00:29:19,059 --> 00:29:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] da razgovaram sa istom ljubavlju

642
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] i sa bratom kršćenom

643
00:29:23,059 --> 00:29:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] s kojime veže Isus Kristi,

644
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] oni to drugi znaju,

645
00:29:26,019 --> 00:29:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] da nema drugog mog pogleda,

646
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] druge geste,

647
00:29:31,299 --> 00:29:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] druge boje glasa.

648
00:29:33,019 --> 00:29:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nema, kad razgovaram sa njima,

649
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] identičan sam.

650
00:29:36,220 --> 00:29:37,299
[SPEAKER_00] Sjeđam se,

651
00:29:37,299 --> 00:29:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam gospodinu,

652
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:43,339
[SPEAKER_00] ako je to tvoj glas u mome srcu,

653
00:29:43,339 --> 00:29:44,660
[SPEAKER_00] ako to ti govoriš,

654
00:29:44,660 --> 00:29:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] ako to ti želiš,

655
00:29:45,819 --> 00:29:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] razumski znam,

656
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] to je najbolje za mene.

657
00:29:49,599 --> 00:29:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] i pristajem na to,

658
00:29:51,519 --> 00:29:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] hoću,

659
00:29:52,059 --> 00:29:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] ali bojim se.

660
00:29:53,339 --> 00:29:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sjećam se da sam fizičku bol na srcu osjetio.

661
00:29:57,599 --> 00:29:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] Baš bol na srcu,

662
00:29:59,099 --> 00:30:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] stezanje,

663
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] pulsiranje srca,

664
00:30:02,019 --> 00:30:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] stezanje,

665
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:03,640
[SPEAKER_00] puštanje,

666
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,279
[SPEAKER_00] stezanje,

667
00:30:04,279 --> 00:30:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] kao da neki kamen otišao.

668
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:07,839
[SPEAKER_00] Proplakao sam još malo,

669
00:30:07,839 --> 00:30:09,240
[SPEAKER_00] baš ja volim plakat,

670
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:11,859
[SPEAKER_00] kao ovoga veliki motivac i romantičar,

671
00:30:11,859 --> 00:30:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] i nakon toga ušla jedna takva sloboda o mene.

672
00:30:17,500 --> 00:30:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vam to ne mogu opisati.

673
00:30:19,359 --> 00:30:21,279
[SPEAKER_00] Od toga dana,

674
00:30:21,279 --> 00:30:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] stvari su drugačije.

675
00:30:25,519 --> 00:30:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedna korist za mene,

676
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] korist za evangelizatora,

677
00:30:29,519 --> 00:30:35,240
[SPEAKER_00] žrvanj obiteljskog života koji mijenja srce i pročišćava ljubav.

678
00:30:35,740 --> 00:30:38,839
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo sad kratko samo kakve koristi zajednica ima od toga.

679
00:30:38,839 --> 00:30:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] Najčešće zajednica onaka je kakav je voditelj zajednica.

680
00:30:44,619 --> 00:30:49,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja imam određene kreposti,

681
00:30:49,779 --> 00:30:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] temeljne životne vrijednosti,

682
00:30:52,119 --> 00:30:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] ako imam zdravu komunikaciju,

683
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] jasnoću po nekim bitnim pitanjima,

684
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] zajednica to uzima.

685
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kao djeca što uzimaju od oca i majke.

686
00:31:01,019 --> 00:31:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako,

687
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:03,799
[SPEAKER_00] ranjenosti

688
00:31:03,799 --> 00:31:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] voditelja zajednice prelaze na zajednicu.

689
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:09,200
[SPEAKER_00] U ovom slučaju,

690
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] kada mi ulazimo u slobodu

691
00:31:11,019 --> 00:31:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] od evangelizacije

692
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] kroz tamo vlastite

693
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] bijede,

694
00:31:17,539 --> 00:31:19,200
[SPEAKER_00] iskustvo vlastite bijede,

695
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo

696
00:31:20,619 --> 00:31:23,680
[SPEAKER_00] mi vam počinjemo živjeti

697
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je za mene

698
00:31:24,559 --> 00:31:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] jako, jako lijepo, divno.

699
00:31:27,099 --> 00:31:29,319
[SPEAKER_00] To mi u svetoj obitelji zaista živimo.

700
00:31:29,319 --> 00:31:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo tu milost i sretnjstvo zbog toga.

701
00:31:31,940 --> 00:31:33,680
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazimo do toga

702
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:34,680
[SPEAKER_00] da

703
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek je uvijek ispred zajednice.

704
00:31:39,599 --> 00:31:41,700
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek je ispred zajednice.

705
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:42,740
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

706
00:31:42,740 --> 00:31:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] prilazimo ljudima u zajednici

707
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] kada dolaze nova garnitura djece.

708
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, morate jednu stvar znati za zajednicu.

709
00:31:49,579 --> 00:31:52,200
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto vam bude možda ova priča malo smislenija.

710
00:31:53,259 --> 00:32:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] naši najaktivniji članovi zajednice svi su ljudi, muži, žena, oboje su zajednici, dakle parovi koji imaju mnogobrojnu obitelj, znači više djece.

711
00:32:05,039 --> 00:32:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] I nama svako malo, sad zamislite, imate udarne ljude, evo jedno djete, drugo, treće, četvrto, peto, non stop djeca.

712
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] Male su razlike.

713
00:32:17,619 --> 00:32:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] I, pazi, ti imaš jedan realan problem da ne možeš raditi neki iću neki bum.

714
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo ciljano stali sa radom sa mladima, jer smo bili odgovorni prema njima i ponizni.

715
00:32:30,039 --> 00:32:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] I znali smo, imamo metode kako ih možemo zapaliti, imamo iskustvo.

716
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:36,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ko će se brinit sa njima?

717
00:32:36,299 --> 00:32:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ko ja nisam poravnat sa Rafaelom, Terezom i Rahelom i Dajanom.

718
00:32:40,039 --> 00:32:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ko će se brinit za ove?

719
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] Pa uništitit ću ih.

720
00:32:43,319 --> 00:32:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] Oni će tražit nas, naše vrijeme, a moji ljudi im to ne mogu dati.

721
00:32:47,579 --> 00:32:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] Čekat ćemo, staćemo.

722
00:32:49,980 --> 00:32:53,720
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom, naši primjeri.

723
00:32:53,720 --> 00:33:01,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, dolazi novo djete, kažeš voditi u nekoga tima, preduhitriš ga, pomažeš mu,

724
00:33:01,839 --> 00:33:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] da samo ne mora ja da na početku crljiti kako da to kaže, da će se povuć,

725
00:33:07,059 --> 00:33:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] a tamo smo ušli neki projekt.

726
00:33:09,019 --> 00:33:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, a Bog mu je poremetio taj projekt, da ušli mu djete.

727
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] Čuj, brate, ajde šibaj doma.

728
00:33:18,079 --> 00:33:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] Šibaj doma.

729
00:33:19,259 --> 00:33:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] Budi doma sa svojom obitelji.

730
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:23,359
[SPEAKER_00] Budi u svoju ženu.

731
00:33:23,359 --> 00:33:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ti se djete rodi, budi onoliko koliko je potrebno.

732
00:33:29,539 --> 00:33:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] I ne samo to, šta mogu učinjen za tebe?

733
00:33:32,079 --> 00:33:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ti mogu pomoći?

734
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] Jel ti treba šta?

735
00:33:36,500 --> 00:33:43,200
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo sebi kupovali, kad su naše žene trudne, idemo u nabavke, šopinge,

736
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] donosimo ručkove jedne drugima.

737
00:33:45,099 --> 00:33:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] To su take geste ljubavi koje vas izuvaju iz cipela.

738
00:33:49,039 --> 00:33:51,279
[SPEAKER_00] Izuvaju vas iz cipela.

739
00:33:51,279 --> 00:33:56,680
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je moja žena ležala, moja majka je živa, i njena je mama živa,

740
00:33:56,680 --> 00:34:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] i roditelji su na živi, imamo pomoć, stvarno smo tu blagostavljeni.

741
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:05,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ali uz njih tebi dođe zajednica, braća, sestre, muški,

742
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] donosi ručak, evo buraz, evo.

743
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:10,320
[SPEAKER_00] Evo košara, voča, evo, evo ono.

744
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne treba buraz.

745
00:34:11,780 --> 00:34:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to ubija, to razvara, ono, tvrdo ljudsko srce i mijenja te.

746
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] I što se događa takim pristupom, kad tako pristupamo,

747
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo tako pristupali našim ljudima,

748
00:34:27,679 --> 00:34:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] zanimljivo je da, znate kako na početku malo,

749
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] tako i naravno i kod nas bilo, malo ljudi pobjegnu,

750
00:34:34,719 --> 00:34:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] dođe prvo djete, pa si uplašen, pa si fokusiran skroz na njega,

751
00:34:39,099 --> 00:34:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa ga držiš za sebe, ko malo zlatno tele,

752
00:34:42,539 --> 00:34:47,400
[SPEAKER_00] i onda postaje ti mali bijegov i, ok, tome djete treba

753
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] i tome žena treba.

754
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] I zato se još malo krije, gledaj, nisam opće sposoban,

755
00:34:52,940 --> 00:34:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne želim se trenutno baviti evangelizacijom.

756
00:34:55,380 --> 00:34:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] I to je isto normalno, ok.

757
00:34:57,079 --> 00:35:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon trećeg, četvrtog djeteta,

758
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] u nekim slučajima,

759
00:35:04,239 --> 00:35:06,659
[SPEAKER_00] sad nam se vraćaju,

760
00:35:06,659 --> 00:35:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] sad kad je tek teže,

761
00:35:09,119 --> 00:35:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] u slobodi dirnuti ljubavlju,

762
00:35:12,519 --> 00:35:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] dirnuti zdravim pristupom,

763
00:35:15,659 --> 00:35:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi nam se vraćaju i stavljaju nam se na raspolaganje.

764
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] Stavljaju se, to je, gospodinu na raspolaganje.

765
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, recimo, trenutno naše stanje u zajednici,

766
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] ne, šestdesetak nas je članova,

767
00:35:27,940 --> 00:35:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] nešto malo više,

768
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] da imamo jednu grupu za mame.

769
00:35:33,619 --> 00:35:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] Imam još malo vremena, pet minuta?

770
00:35:36,199 --> 00:35:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] Imao tako, ok.

771
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] Žena moja se brine, pokazuje na sat,

772
00:35:41,340 --> 00:35:42,219
[SPEAKER_00] evo, doslovno pet.

773
00:35:42,219 --> 00:35:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pa ona mene pozna,

774
00:35:46,619 --> 00:35:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] ona zna taj strah,

775
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,639
[SPEAKER_00] onda na početku ode u,

776
00:35:49,639 --> 00:35:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] ako mene ne povuče dole.

777
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:55,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sad imamo grupu za mame,

778
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] žene su se organizirale

779
00:35:57,960 --> 00:36:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] i jednom mjesečnom mole.

780
00:36:00,719 --> 00:36:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Imaju otvorene susete sa sve druge žene.

781
00:36:03,199 --> 00:36:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo grupu za djecu do četiri godine,

782
00:36:07,579 --> 00:36:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se djeca mole.

783
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] Do pete godine grupu od pete godine,

784
00:36:13,699 --> 00:36:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] dječji zbor.

785
00:36:15,019 --> 00:36:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] I uz naše otvorene susete

786
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] imamo obiteljski suset.

787
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sad imamo trenutno vezano za obitelj

788
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] veći sadržaj nego prije.

789
00:36:26,239 --> 00:36:29,639
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sad su u slobodi ljudi došli,

790
00:36:29,639 --> 00:36:31,639
[SPEAKER_00] niko ih nije stiskoo,

791
00:36:31,639 --> 00:36:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] niko im nije dao pritisak

792
00:36:33,099 --> 00:36:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] i to mijenja njihovu,

793
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] to mijenja njihovu sliku o Bogu.

794
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kad takav pristup imate.

795
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:41,219
[SPEAKER_00] I onda u slobodi dolaze,

796
00:36:41,219 --> 00:36:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] kažu,

797
00:36:41,639 --> 00:36:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] evo, gospodine,

798
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] sazrijevaju.

799
00:36:44,599 --> 00:36:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I evo, za kraj,

800
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] u takvom pristupu,

801
00:36:48,739 --> 00:36:50,679
[SPEAKER_00] kada ulazimo u to iskustvo,

802
00:36:50,679 --> 00:36:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] iz tog iskustva,

803
00:36:51,739 --> 00:36:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] nemoći idemo u tu slobodu,

804
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] postajemo maleni,

805
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] postajemo smireni

806
00:36:57,360 --> 00:37:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] i počinjemo doživljavati čovjeka.

807
00:37:00,380 --> 00:37:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kad počneš čovjeka doživljavati

808
00:37:02,059 --> 00:37:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] svakog čovjeka

809
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] jednakom pažnjom i ljubavlju,

810
00:37:05,599 --> 00:37:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] ulazimo,

811
00:37:07,599 --> 00:37:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam to nazvao,

812
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] u zdravu komunikaciju.

813
00:37:10,039 --> 00:37:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zdrava komunikacija

814
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] gdje nema podrazumijevanja.

815
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:15,179
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte,

816
00:37:15,179 --> 00:37:16,719
[SPEAKER_00] možete vidjeti u svojima obiteljima

817
00:37:16,719 --> 00:37:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] koji ste u braku,

818
00:37:17,780 --> 00:37:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] kad ste mužu, žene

819
00:37:19,659 --> 00:37:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili muževi,

820
00:37:21,179 --> 00:37:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad ste ženama rekli da ih volite.

821
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ste im rekli hvala ti,

822
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] hvala ti za ovaj ručak,

823
00:37:27,380 --> 00:37:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] hvala ti še si tako dobra mama,

824
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] hvala ti še si moja žena.

825
00:37:30,659 --> 00:37:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mi to ne govorimo

826
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] nakon nekog vremena

827
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] ili se to podrazumijeva.

828
00:37:35,500 --> 00:37:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] A podrazumijevanje

829
00:37:38,380 --> 00:37:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] ubija ljubav.

830
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kad si rekao članu

831
00:37:41,039 --> 00:37:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] svoje zajednice,

832
00:37:42,019 --> 00:37:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] hvala ti,

833
00:37:43,099 --> 00:37:45,559
[SPEAKER_00] hvala ti što si tu sa mnom,

834
00:37:45,559 --> 00:37:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] što te imam,

835
00:37:46,539 --> 00:37:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] tako je lijepo

836
00:37:48,059 --> 00:37:49,639
[SPEAKER_00] s tobom donositi Krista.

837
00:37:49,639 --> 00:37:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] Može da zlučiti očudno,

838
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] mi tako komuniciramo

839
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:54,679
[SPEAKER_00] sve toj obitelji.

840
00:37:54,679 --> 00:37:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] To je nama prirodno postalo,

841
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,739
[SPEAKER_00] normalno.

842
00:37:57,739 --> 00:38:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sine, šta mogu učiniti za tebe?

843
00:38:00,940 --> 00:38:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ti u školi?

844
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] ili imaš nekih problema?

845
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ti je sa drugom djecom?

846
00:38:04,539 --> 00:38:06,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dobra komunikacija?

847
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:08,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se osjećaš?

848
00:38:08,300 --> 00:38:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] Bio si na prvom treningu?

849
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,280
[SPEAKER_00] Je li sve bilo ok?

850
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ili imaš osjećaja

851
00:38:13,099 --> 00:38:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] da nisi dobar?

852
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] Je li te to muči?

853
00:38:16,679 --> 00:38:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što se događa?

854
00:38:17,579 --> 00:38:17,579
[UNKNOWN] Znate što se događa?

855
00:38:17,579 --> 00:38:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Povratna reakcija.

856
00:38:18,559 --> 00:38:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sin u prvom razredu,

857
00:38:20,079 --> 00:38:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] Rafija sa drugi razred,

858
00:38:21,219 --> 00:38:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi do mene i dane,

859
00:38:22,820 --> 00:38:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] ovakvim načinom našeg obiteljske komunikacije,

860
00:38:25,820 --> 00:38:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] formiranje na taj način i kaže,

861
00:38:28,300 --> 00:38:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] čuj, tate, mama,

862
00:38:30,619 --> 00:38:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] imam jednu situaciju,

863
00:38:32,420 --> 00:38:33,699
[SPEAKER_00] treba mi vaš savjet, kaže.

864
00:38:35,659 --> 00:38:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ego, reci sine,

865
00:38:36,719 --> 00:38:39,679
[SPEAKER_00] pa evo, ne znam kak se postaviti u tom, tom i tom.

866
00:38:39,679 --> 00:38:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] I sad nama nabraja.

867
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kao roditelji do suza budemo ganuti,

868
00:38:44,940 --> 00:38:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] zahvalni Bogu,

869
00:38:46,019 --> 00:38:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] jer vidimo Bog je živ

870
00:38:47,639 --> 00:38:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] i dobro vodi naš obitelj.

871
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ta zdrava komunikacija nosi mnogo bodova,

872
00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] nosi mnogo blagoslova.

873
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] Taj život u obitelji,

874
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad i žrvni obitelji,

875
00:38:58,920 --> 00:39:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo poravnati s Božijom voljom,

876
00:39:01,599 --> 00:39:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] da tu umirem do kraja,

877
00:39:04,619 --> 00:39:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] iz toga idem van,

878
00:39:05,900 --> 00:39:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] iz stadičkih svojih dužnosti,

879
00:39:08,019 --> 00:39:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] to je kao na onom ispitu,

880
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] nekom stručnom,

881
00:39:11,539 --> 00:39:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] imate jedno pitanje donosi pet bodova,

882
00:39:15,579 --> 00:39:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] a jedno pitanje donosi deset bodova.

883
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] I nama nekad pitamo se

884
00:39:20,059 --> 00:39:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] šta nam fali evangelizaciju,

885
00:39:21,579 --> 00:39:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] ne imamo dovoljno bodova,

886
00:39:22,820 --> 00:39:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslova do kraja.

887
00:39:24,059 --> 00:39:28,179
[SPEAKER_00] A evo, tu se kriju ti dodatni bodovi,

888
00:39:28,179 --> 00:39:28,940
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslovi.

889
00:39:28,940 --> 00:39:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] Obitelje,

890
00:39:33,579 --> 00:39:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] kad počnemo se njoj davati,

891
00:39:37,039 --> 00:39:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] živjeti za nju,

892
00:39:38,179 --> 00:39:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] obitelj je sigurno utočište.

893
00:39:40,539 --> 00:39:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljstvo Božje je među nama,

894
00:39:42,579 --> 00:39:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] mjesto gdje postaje

895
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] najbolja verzija sebe,

896
00:39:46,579 --> 00:39:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] gdje smijem bit slab

897
00:39:48,119 --> 00:39:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam degradiran,

898
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] nek sam i dalje voljen,

899
00:39:51,599 --> 00:39:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] gdje mogu biti onda

900
00:39:53,619 --> 00:39:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] pravo jak.

901
00:39:56,739 --> 00:39:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] i evo,

902
00:39:57,940 --> 00:39:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] samo još misla za one koji imaju djecu,

903
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] kad ono,

904
00:40:03,199 --> 00:40:05,820
[SPEAKER_00] uđem u naviku odbijanja djece,

905
00:40:05,820 --> 00:40:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] da nemoj sad,

906
00:40:06,599 --> 00:40:06,900
[SPEAKER_00] da je ovo,

907
00:40:06,900 --> 00:40:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] ili brzo mu nešto odgovorim,

908
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] ne sa zanimanjem,

909
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:12,920
[SPEAKER_00] svijetite se,

910
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] da Bog vam

911
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] kroz djecu pokazuje

912
00:40:17,159 --> 00:40:18,340
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ste posebni,

913
00:40:18,340 --> 00:40:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] koliko vas voli.

914
00:40:21,019 --> 00:40:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] djeca idu sa takvim zanimanjem prema vama

915
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] i kad bi smo mi

916
00:40:27,119 --> 00:40:31,679
[SPEAKER_00] sa takvom čežnjom išli prema Bogu,

917
00:40:31,679 --> 00:40:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] kao što djeca idu prema nama,

918
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:37,159
[SPEAKER_00] o kako bi imali čudesan odnos sa gospodinom.

919
00:40:37,159 --> 00:40:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi imali čudesan odnos sa gospodinom.

920
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato evo,

921
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] dajte svoje djeci koji imate

922
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] dan djece pažnju,

923
00:40:47,039 --> 00:40:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] koju zavrijeđuju

924
00:40:48,739 --> 00:40:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjet ćete kakve će gospodin

925
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] činiti stvari.

926
00:40:53,139 --> 00:40:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, hvala vam.

